description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nAbsorbs the enemy's MP when attacking with Magic skills, until it reaches 0.
description.name: MP Eater

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nUse the arrow keys to teleport to other places in the same map on a set distance.
description.name: Teleport

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nRecovers the HP of all party members around the area. The amount of healing depends on the number of people being healed, and the undead monster in the vicinity of this will receive damage.
description.name: Heal

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nTemporarily decreases the weapon damage received. It has no effect, however, on the magic attack.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 5 on Heal#
description.name: Invincible

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 20]\nTemporarily increases the weapon def., magic def., accuracy, and avoidability of all party members around the area. This cannot be combined with a skill or a potion.\nRequired Skill : #cAt least Level 5 on Invincible#
description.name: Bless

description.desc: [마스터 레벨 : 30]\nAttacks a single monster by firing Holy Arrows.  Very effective against the undead's or devil-based monsters.
description.name: Holy Arrow
